<a class="title" href="/nodes/96380/comments/1407659">Re: Dédommagement != espérance de gain</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/littleboy" rel="author">Littleboy</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-13T07:51:08+01:00"><span class="date">le 13/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 07:51</span></time>.
