<li class="comment even score0" id="comment-1409961">
<h2>
<a class="parent" href="/users/vnvps/journaux/enfin--3#comment-1408506" title="Aller au commentaire parent">[^]</a>
<a class="anchor" href="/users/vnvps/journaux/enfin--3#comment-1409961" title="Lien direct vers ce commentaire">#</a>
 
<a class="title" href="/nodes/96380/comments/1409961">Re: Vive l&#39;occasion</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/pseudo_debile" rel="author">pseudo_debile</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-11-19T15:31:58+01:00"><span class="date">le 19/11/12</span> <span class="time">à 15:31</span></time>.
